-----------------------------------------------------------------
To see the ads volume for your ad account:
-----------------------------------------------------------------


curl -G \
-d "access_token=<access_token>" \
"https://graph.facebook.com/<API_VERSION>/act_<ad_account_ID>/ads_volume"




